{"tid":1617273,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"[ 香城online ] 狼人罷工法","createTime":"2019-10-03T17:05:49.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-03T17:08:53.000Z","uid":258321,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"a7ed1ed812222916d7d0331e57f146c6be6533fd","tid":1617273,"uid":258321,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-03T17:05:49.000Z","msg":"罷工既人最怕孤獨 但係又怕被人篤灰搞到相認唔到 於是就人人都唔罷 繼續平行時空<br />\n所以我諗匿名搵fd子+互相監控會唔會就有人敢罷?<br />\n<br />\n有個構思 但係需要大channel admin幫手做監察<br />\n構思係咁:<br />\n有心人開TG group =&gt; po員工證俾bot =&gt; 放group link字條係office公用地方(不起眼位置 e.g. pantry 某角落) =&gt; 入group須po員工證俾bot(遮淨小小野 e.g. 名既其中一隻字) =&gt; 相認罷工<br />\n<br />\n機制:<br />\n用bot po員工證，channel admin有access right，group member懷疑被篤灰 =&gt; 同bot講 =&gt; 全部member選出嫌疑人(好似玩狼人咁) =&gt; Channel起25仔底做9佢<br />\n全城定一個時間一齊貼紙仔同入group deadline"},{"pid":"1cbba0280d76feebacac529502a5fd9116d26b7f","tid":1617273,"uid":258321,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-03T17:06:20.000Z","msg":"推唔到照推"},{"pid":"2945b1ba1cb1adedc7a4681aec9919bf3e2d997e","tid":1617273,"uid":258321,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-03T17:06:35.000Z","msg":"推唔到照推"},{"pid":"3d147a7885979c77fa174049a7734a62bc0c235b","tid":1617273,"uid":123440,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-03T17:08:53.000Z","msg":"有陣自己友嘅文革除了<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}